NPCDialogue.LocalizedString: GNARLY! MOONBEARD'S POTIONS ALWAYS DO THE JOB!

WELL OK. @WHAT WE HAVE BEFORE US HERE, JOT MY DUDE, IS A WALL OF IRONWEED. @IT'S THE TOUGHEST, GNARLIEST PLANT YOU WILL EVER ENCOUNTER. @IT'S USUALLY KEPT AT BAY BY THE RIGHTEOUS GARDENERS OF TRARRG. @BUT... THE GARDENERS ARE MIA. SO THE IRONWEED IS BIB. @THAT'S 'BACK IN BUSINESS', DUDE.

HELLO, HIKERS! @IRONWEED, EH? TOUGH SHRUB. @I THINK I CAN HELP YOU OUT. I COOK UP A MEAN WEEDKILLER. @BUT I NEED A SPECIAL INGREDIENT... A CRUSHROOM! @IT'S... LIKE A PURPLE MUSHROOM. LUCKILY, THEY OFTEN GROW NEAR IRONWEED. @IF YOU GET ME ONE I MIGHT BE ABLE TO RUSTLE UP SOMETHING! @MOONBEARD OUT!

OH GOOD ONE... YOU GOT A CRUSHROOM! @HAND IT OVER, LAD! @... @OH. WE'RE HUNDREDS OF MILES APART. @BIT OF A WRINKLE IN THE PLAN, THAT. @WELL... MAYBE THERE'S A WAY YOU COULD SHORTCUT ALL THOSE MILES TO GET ME THAT 'SHROOM?
